360-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Yes. WordPress websites are responsive, but not all. The responsive capability of a WordPress website depends on the theme and the plugins that you are using. Let\'s take a look at how your choice of theme and plugins can effect the overall responsiveness of your website.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><p> <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-websites-responsive/#more-59360\" class=\"more-link\">Read More</a></p><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-websites-responsive/\">Are WordPress Websites Responsive?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-websites-responsive/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"13\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"Introducing the Accordion Widget\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-accordion-widget/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-accordion-widget/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 11 Oct 2017 08:29:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://siteorigin.com/?p=69287\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:572:\"<p>Accordions are a great way to organise your pages. Whether you’re creating a frequently asked question page, a services page or just a general information page &#8211; accordions help you fit a lot of information into a small amount of space. In the Widgets Bundle 1.10.0 update, we’re introducing a brand new, powerful Accordion Widget. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-accordion-widget/\">Introducing the Accordion Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Greg Priday\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5775:\"<p>Accordions are a great way to organise your pages. Whether you’re creating a frequently asked question page, a services page or just a general information page &#8211; accordions help you fit a lot of information into a small amount of space.</p>\n<p>In the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/\">Widgets Bundle</a> 1.10.0 update, we’re introducing a brand new, powerful Accordion Widget. Allowing you to add accordions to your <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder/\">Page Builder</a> pages or the many <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-beaver-builder-elementor/\">other page builder plugins</a> that the Widgets Bundle supports.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-69287\"></span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_69315\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-69315 size-large\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-699x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-699x395.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-300x169.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-768x434.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-313x177.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-600x339.png 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion-400x225.png 400w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/default-accordion.png 1013w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">The default accordion style.</p>\n</div>\n<p>As always, this is a completely free addon. All you need to do is update your copy of Widgets Bundle, then navigate to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span></span> in your WordPress admin and activate the accordion widget.</p>\n<p>It’s definitely worth checking out this new widget. We’ve posted some <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/accordion-widget/\">Accordion Widget documentation</a> to help you get started.</p>\n<h3>Something Extra for Premium Users</h3>\n<p>Of course, we’re always looking for ways to make things even better for our <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> users. We’re also giving all our Premium users access to an advanced accordion addon that adds a whole bunch of extra features.</p>\n<p>The free Accordion widget lets you add standard TinyMCE text content, but in the premium addon, we’re giving you the power to create accordion content using a layout field. This means you can fill your accordions with complex widgets and Page Builder style layouts.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_69316\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-69316\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion-699x351.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion-699x351.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion-300x150.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion-768x385.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion-313x157.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion-600x301.png 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/layout-builder-accordion.png 1027w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Create content using a layout builder</p>\n</div>\n<p>Our design team also worked hard on creating a set of visual customization settings for your widgets that allow you to create a huge number of different designs. As an added bonus, next week we’ll be releasing another update that includes some beautifully designed presets.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_69439\" style=\"width: 3256px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-69439\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"3246\" height=\"686\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs.png 3246w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-300x63.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-768x162.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-699x148.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-1050x222.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-313x66.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-600x127.png 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/accordion-designs-1200x254.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3246px) 100vw, 3246px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Some of the design variations possible with SiteOrigin Premium</p>\n</div>\n<p>If you aren’t a <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> member yet, be sure to sign up. It’s a cost-effective way to build your sites faster and more professionally. We’re introducing more addons all the time, so the longer you’re a member, the more valuable it becomes.</p>\n<p>A demo of the above designs is available <a href=\"http://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/accordion-addon/\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-accordion-widget/\">Introducing the Accordion Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-accordion-widget/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"47\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Are WordPress Themes Customizable?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-themes-customizable/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-themes-customizable/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 26 Sep 2017 10:58:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://siteorigin.com/?p=59631\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:601:\"<p>WordPress themes can be customized in several ways depending on the extent to which you are wanting to change your themes look and feel. From powerful theme customization settings built right into the WordPress Customizer, to add-on plugins and real-time CSS Editors like SiteOrigin CSS. WordPress Customizer Any well-designed WordPress theme will offer a variety of [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-themes-customizable/\">Are WordPress Themes Customizable?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Ian Rossiter\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9655:\"<p>WordPress themes can be customized in several ways depending on the extent to which you are wanting to change your themes look and feel. From powerful theme customization settings built right into the WordPress Customizer, to add-on plugins and real-time CSS Editors like <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/css/\">SiteOrigin CSS</a>.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-59631\"></span></p>\n<h2>WordPress Customizer</h2>\n<p>Any well-designed WordPress theme will offer a variety of basic styling and layout customization options built directly into the WordPress customizer. Most themes will offer the ability to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Upload retina logos</li>\n<li>Specify a variety of color settings in areas such as headers, navigation, footers and page backgrounds</li>\n<li>Choose your favourite google fonts for headings and body text, as well as adjust font colors</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-59650 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations.jpg\" alt=\"Using the WordPress customizer to customize your theme\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations.jpg 1920w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-300x169.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-768x432.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-699x393.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-1050x591.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-313x176.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-600x338.jpg 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-340x190.jpg 340w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-400x225.jpg 400w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Basic-Customizations-800x450.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Customizable Fonts</strong></p>\n<p>If you are looking for more than just the basic customizations, then search for themes that are advertised to be <strong>multi-purpose</strong>, such as <a href=\"https://themetrust.com/themes/create/?ref=2194&amp;campaign=theme-page\">Create</a> by ThemeTrust or <a href=\"https://themify.me/member/aff/go/ibrossiter/?cr=aHR0cHM6Ly90aGVtaWZ5Lm1lL3RoZW1lcy91bHRyYQ==\">Ultra</a> by Themify. Multi-purpose themes usually offer more advanced styling and layout options. For example, in addition to the settings above, <a href=\"https://themetrust.com/themes/create/?ref=2194&amp;campaign=theme-page\">Create</a> also offers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multiple header layouts enabling variety of logo positions</li>\n<li>Boxed and full-width layouts</li>\n<li>Specific settings for individual pages, posts, and projects</li>\n<li>Multi-page and one-page menu navigation</li>\n<li>Mega menus</li>\n<li>3rd party plugin integrations such as Woocommerce</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Some themes may also offer the ability to switch from a horizontal menu to a sidebar menu structure.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-59656 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed.jpg\" alt=\"multi-purpose themes offer more customization options\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed.jpg 1920w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-300x169.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-768x432.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-699x393.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-1050x591.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-313x176.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-600x338.jpg 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-340x190.jpg 340w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-400x225.jpg 400w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Boxed-800x450.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://themetrust.com/themes/create/?ref=2194&amp;campaign=theme-page\">Create</a> Multi-Purpose WordPress Theme &#8211; Layout Setting</strong></p>\n<h2>Plugins</h2>\n<p>WordPress plugins are another great way to customize a WordPress Theme by adding additional functionality. Themes are often built around and/or come bundled with custom or 3rd Party plugins to enhance their default offering. Typically bundled plugins include <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder/\">Page Builders</a>, Sliders, Contact Forms, Woocommerce, and a variety of custom or 3rd party widgets such as SiteOrigin <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/\">Widgets Bundle</a>.</p>\n<h2>Demo Content</h2>\n<p>If you are lucky, you may find a theme that includes a variety of demo content, adding another layer of customizability altogether and giving you a head start on your content creation. Again, take a look at <a href=\"https://themetrust.com/themes/create/?ref=2194&amp;campaign=theme-page\">Create</a> by ThemeTrust or <a href=\"http://proteusthemes.sjv.io/c/269244/339749/5085?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.proteusthemes.com%2Fwordpress-themes%2Fbolts-construction%2F\">Bolts</a> by ProteusThemes. They are both great examples of how demo content can offer you added customization.</p>\n<h2>CSS Editors</h2>\n<p>If you are looking for styling customizability beyond what your theme can offer, then take a look at <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/css/\">SiteOrigin CSS</a>. It is a powerful CSS editor that allows you to change your WordPress website&#8217;s design in real-time by adding your custom css code to your themes default styling.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-59661 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS.jpg\" alt=\"SiteOrigin CSS is a powerful CSS editor\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS.jpg 1920w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-300x169.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-768x432.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-699x393.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-1050x591.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-313x176.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-600x338.jpg 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-340x190.jpg 340w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-400x225.jpg 400w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SiteOrigin-CSS-800x450.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/css/\"><b>SiteOrigin CSS</b></a> <strong>Editor</strong></p>\n<h2>Child Themes</h2>\n<p>If you are a confident CSS and PHP developer, you can also go about creating a Child Theme. First you need to find a theme that is closest to what you are looking for, this is called the &#8220;Parent&#8221; theme. You can then add the additional styling and functionality by creating your own style.css and functions.php files. These files will form the basis of your Child Theme, referencing the Parent Theme for its core styling and functionality. Check out this article by <a href=\"https://themify.me/member/aff/go/ibrossiter/?cr=aHR0cHM6Ly90aGVtaWZ5Lm1lL2RvY3MvY2hpbGQtdGhlbWU=\">Themify</a> for a step by guide.</p>\n<p>So, when looking for powerful theme customizability, make sure you search for multi-purpose themes. Check on the themes listed features for the customization settings listed above and also look to see what plugins come bundled, and what additional 3rd party plugins they support.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-59659 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page.jpg\" alt=\"check themes key features for listed customisability options\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page.jpg 1920w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-300x169.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-768x432.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-699x393.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-1050x591.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-313x176.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-600x338.jpg 600w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-340x190.jpg 340w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-400x225.jpg 400w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/features-page-800x450.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Themes Key Features</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-themes-customizable/\">Are WordPress Themes Customizable?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://siteorigin.com/wordpress-themes-customizable/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Page Builder Cell Vertical Alignment\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder-cell-vertical-alignment/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"